channel.title: M.a.g
channel.description:
Stands for Massive Action Game. The game promises 256 player online matches. The 256 people will be divided into 8 parties. It is said to be a FPS and also a PS3 exclusive. Looks super hot to me.
Beta is scheduled for midsummer and the release of the actual game is scheduled for Fall.

http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RadpFEwtTSE&feature=related (no dubs)
